When filling in a blank cell, if I accidentally touch the wrong number but slide my finger to a neighboring number without lifting it, the initially touched number still gets entered. This causes me to lose points due to a misclick, even when I could have avoided the mistake. I would greatly appreciate it if, in future versions, the number that is registered could be based on the number where the finger is released, rather than the initial touch.
